anime.title: Attack on Titan
anime.description: In a world where humanity lives within cities surrounded by enormous walls due to the Titans, giant humanoid beings who devour humans seemingly without reason.

anime.title: Demon Slayer
anime.description: A youth begins a quest to fight demons and save his sister after his family is slaughtered and his sister is turned into a demon.

anime.title: My Hero Academia
anime.description: In a world where people with superpowers known as 'Quirks' are the norm, a boy without powers dreams of becoming a superhero.

anime.title: One Piece
anime.description: Follows the adventures of Monkey D. Luffy and his pirate crew in order to find the greatest treasure ever left by the legendary Pirate, Gold Roger.

anime.title: Death Note
anime.description: An intelligent high school student goes on a secret crusade to eliminate criminals from the world after discovering a notebook capable of killing anyone whose name is written into it.

anime.title: Fullmetal Alchemist: Brotherhood
anime.description: Two brothers search for a Philosopher's Stone after an attempt to revive their deceased mother goes wrong and leaves them in damaged physical forms.

anime.title: Naruto
anime.description: Naruto Uzumaki, a mischievous adolescent ninja, struggles as he searches for recognition and dreams of becoming the Hokage, the village's leader and strongest ninja.

anime.title: Jujutsu Kaisen
anime.description: A boy swallows a cursed talisman - the finger of a demon - and becomes cursed himself. He enters a shaman's school to be able to locate the demon's other body parts and thus exorcise himself.

anime.title: Dragon Ball Z
anime.description: After learning that he is from another planet, a warrior named Goku and his friends are challenged by an array of powerful aliens.

anime.title: Tokyo Ghoul
anime.description: A Tokyo college student is attacked by a ghoul, a superpowered human who feeds on human flesh. He survives, but has become part ghoul and becomes a fugitive on the run.

anime.title: One Punch Man
anime.description: The story of Saitama, a hero that does it for fun & can defeat his enemies with a single punch.

anime.title: Sword Art Online
anime.description: In the near future, players of a virtual reality MMORPG are trapped inside the game and must fight to survive.

anime.title: Hunter x Hunter
anime.description: Gon Freecss aspires to become a Hunter, an exceptional being capable of greatness. With his friends and his potential, he seeks out his father, who left him when he was younger.

anime.title: Black Clover
anime.description: Asta and Yuno were abandoned together at the same church and have been inseparable since. As children, they promised that they would compete against each other to see who would become the next Emperor Magus.

anime.title: Steins;Gate
anime.description: A self-proclaimed mad scientist discovers a way to alter the past through text messages, leading to dire consequences.

anime.title: Code Geass
anime.description: After being given a mysterious power to control others, an exiled prince returns to seek revenge on those who murdered his mother and punish his father.

anime.title: Chainsaw Man
anime.description: Following a betrayal, a young man left for dead is reborn as a powerful devil-human hybrid after merging with his pet devil and is soon enlisted by a government agency to hunt down evil devils.

anime.title: Bleach
anime.description: High school student Ichigo Kurosaki, who has the ability to see ghosts, gains soul reaper powers from Rukia Kuchiki and sets out to save the world from 'Hollows'.

anime.title: Death Parade
anime.description: After death, humans go to either heaven or hell. But for some, at the instant of their death, they arrive at the Quindecim, a bar attended by the mysterious white-haired Decim.

anime.title: Mob Psycho 100
anime.description: A psychic middle school boy tries to live a normal life and keep his growing powers under control, even though he constantly gets into trouble.
